Get up.

00:20:06.920 --> 00:20:07.600
Get up.

00:20:08.400 --> 00:20:10.090
You stole my baby?

00:20:10.440 --> 00:20:12.200
It was the Hole Ghost, to be precise.

00:20:12.680 --> 00:20:14.230
The Hole Ghost stole your baby.

00:20:15.030 --> 00:20:17.600
Then, he pretended to be a Heavenly Tutor and sent him back.

00:20:18.070 --> 00:20:20.030
Their purpose is to make money.

00:20:21.600 --> 00:20:22.520
Do you remember

00:20:22.520 --> 00:20:23.990
what he asked you to do last night?

00:20:25.030 --> 00:20:27.920
