Physician Fu, I'm sorry.

00:23:25.240 --> 00:23:26.080
It's all my fault.

00:23:26.600 --> 00:23:28.440
I overheard your conversation with the chief

00:23:28.750 --> 00:23:30.310
and told Immortal Qin.

00:23:30.990 --> 00:23:32.950
I didn't expect to be taken advantage of by him.

00:23:33.790 --> 00:23:35.470
That's why we're here today.

00:23:36.990 --> 00:23:38.400
I thought I was going to die today.

00:23:38.550 --> 00:23:41.080
I didn't expect you to save my life.

00:23:41.750 --> 00:23:44.310
Physician Fu, I'm really sorry.

00:23:46.400 --> 00:23:47.680
You don't have to.

00:23:48.200 --> 00:23:49.340
You had an asthma attack.

00:23:49.400 --> 00:23:51.160
You're lucky to be alive.

00:23:51.990 --> 00:23:52.790
Get up, Tian Yu.

00:24:02.360 --> 00:24:03.360
